{"tid":1526641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［機場］都係果句，幫唔幫外國人？","createTime":"2019-09-01T06:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T08:26:11.000Z","uid":231342,"like":354,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"9305a2396212ba0eb6ecb8fb90f5a08b741d6409","tid":1526641,"uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:44:18.000Z","msg":"下次搞再機場唔該幫下啲旅客<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n做好文宣，當你幫到人既時候人地先會對我地印象深刻<br />\n而會幫返我地帶走個message!<br />\n如果政府cancel晒所有機<br />\n都唔會係我哋嘅錯。因為起碼我哋有幫佢地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有啲乜嘢可以做？</span><br />\n可以幫佢哋帶路 比佢哋知道係邊度可以排隊或者走<br />\n沿途解釋返俾佢聽我哋做緊啲乜嘢"},{"pid":"edd270927717c02792809f6d72208380b0f34704","tid":1526641,"uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"45d2f015d2622fb6a44380aa18aae1a70401a206","tid":1526641,"uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"64369e30d4eda8699608e6b778ae6df2d749ae7e","tid":1526641,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2cf01e11b1e51d3d1000fc5149350267edba03ac","tid":1526641,"uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:45:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"170acfebf76fdd7b4550a73d144fe1ccc41063f7","tid":1526641,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"#chinazi"},{"pid":"223f0d82dade7785726574d671fc3a6f495f5a43","tid":1526641,"uid":312461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:45:18.000Z","msg":"推推，入機場"},{"pid":"aad574a9f8bbb8d09ba2adb3c6d87540b04cab45","tid":1526641,"uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"339b9ae8fe0e4091c2543bf84274c1423fce6